  "instructions": [
    "Place the lotus leaf wrap on a flat surface with the shiny side facing down.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the lemon juice, garlic, coarse black pepper, and salt.",
    "Arrange the chopped parsley and chopped dill on one half of the lotus leaf wrap, leaving a 1-inch border around the edges.",
    "Crush the bouillon cubes and sprinkle them over the herbs.",
    "Add the diced celery and diced onion on top of the herbs.",
    "Spread the sour cream over the vegetables.",
    "Fold the lotus leaf wrap in half over the filling, pressing the edges to seal.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
